<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="写给手绘新人！4 招教你如何参考照片" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-382832" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hand-painted-course-17-20200803-17.jpg" width="800" height="302" /></span></p>
<p>嘻嘻，心动的你一定想知道大家的学后水平究竟如何吧？</p>
<p>下面是部分学员作业：</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="写给手绘新人！4 招教你如何参考照片" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-382833" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hand-painted-course-17-20200803-18.jpg" width="800" height="800" /></span></p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="写给手绘新人！4 招教你如何参考照片" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-382834" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hand-painted-course-17-20200803-19.jpg" width="800" height="800" /></span></p>
