<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="写给手绘新人！4 招教你如何参考照片" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-382838" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hand-painted-course-17-20200803-23.jpg" width="800" height="800" /></span></p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="写给手绘新人！4 招教你如何参考照片" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-382839" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hand-painted-course-17-20200803-24.jpg" width="800" height="800" /></span></p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="写给手绘新人！4 招教你如何参考照片" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-382840" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hand-painted-course-17-20200803-25.jpg" width="800" height="800" /></span></p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="写给手绘新人！4 招教你如何参考照片" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-382841" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hand-painted-course-17-20200803-26.jpg" width="800" height="800" /></span></p>
<p>△ 闪屏插画</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="写给手绘新人！4 招教你如何参考照片" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-382842" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hand-painted-course-17-20200803-27.jpg" width="800" height="1600" /></span></p>
<p>△ 人物肖像插画</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="写给手绘新人！4 招教你如何参考照片" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-382843" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hand-painted-course-17-20200803-28.jpg" width="800" height="1600" /></span></p>
<p>△ 潮玩趣味卡通</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="写给手绘新人！4 招教你如何参考照片" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-382844" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hand-painted-course-17-20200803-29.jpg" width="800" height="1200" /></span></p>
