<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="写给手绘新人！4 招教你如何参考照片" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-382845" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hand-painted-course-17-20200803-30.jpg" width="800" height="1200" /></span></p>
<p>△ 美食主题插画</p>
